STRING database

Downloaded at: https://string-db.org/cgi/download?species_text=Mus+musculus

library(dplyr)
library(tidygraph)
library(ggraph)
setwd("/home/guestA/n70275b")
dfc <- readr::read_csv("work/fujii/dfcs_w.csv",col_types="_cdc") %>% rename(gene=ext_gene)
Missing column names filled in: 'X1' [1]
deg <- readr::read_csv("work/fujii/DEG_sc.csv") %>% rename(gene=ext_gene)

─ Column specification ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
cols(
  ext_gene = col_character(),
  baseMean = col_double(),
  log2FoldChange = col_double(),
  lfcSE = col_double(),
  stat = col_double(),
  pvalue = col_double(),
  padj = col_double(),
  log10FDR = col_double(),
  PN = col_logical(),
  weight = col_double(),
  class = col_character()
)
st <- readr::read_delim("~/fuji/10090.protein.links.full.v11.0.txt",delim=" ")
ann <- readr::read_tsv("/home/guestA/n70275b/work/fujii/string/10090.protein.info.v11.0.txt.gz",col_types="cc__") %>% with(setNames(preferred_name,protein_external_id))
stg <- st %>% mutate_at(1:2,~ann[.])
g <- as_tbl_graph(stg,directed=FALSE) %>% rename(gene=name) %E>% distinct
s <- g %N>% inner_join(dfc) %>% mutate(sgn=if_else(weight>0,"+","-"))
Joining, by = "gene"
u <- deg %>% top_n(108,abs(stat)) %>% inner_join(activate(g,nodes),.) %>%
  mutate(weight=log2FoldChange,sgn=ifelse(log2FoldChange>0,"+","-"))
Joining, by = "gene"

dfc.string <- plotg(s,cond)
ggsave(file="~/fuji/work/Logireg/paper/stringnet.pdf", dfc.string, units = "in", width = 7, height = 4)
